# threatmodel.md is operator-local. The threat model names open
# Critical/High findings + the attack-path framing for the codebase;
# we deliberately don't ship that to a public repo. Operators keep
# their own copy at /threatmodel.md and pass it to security-sensitive
# review sessions out of band. See AGENTS.md for the discovery
# convention.
threatmodel.md
*.swp
*.swo

